pyargparse: pyargparse (Python Command Line Parsing)
pyargparse:
pyargparse: The argparse module makes it easy to write user-friendly command-line
pyargparse: interfaces. The program defines what arguments it requires, and argparse
pyargparse: will figure out how to parse those out of sys.argv. The argparse module
pyargparse: also automatically generates help and usage messages and issues errors
pyargparse: when users give the program invalid arguments.
pyargparse:
pyargparse: URL: http://code.google.com/p/argparse/
